::'''Xueyi:''' (Trailblazer), the Shackling Prison is still trying to have peace and order restored. It is not safe, so please try not to wander around.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't worry. I can take care of myself.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502100003-->
:::'''Xueyi:''' I wouldn't be worried if I could turn into a cycrane and come back either.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm sure you'll keep me safe.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502100005-->
:::'''Xueyi:''' You may be asking too much of a defenseless little cycrane like me.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502100006-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502100006-->
::'''Xueyi:''' ...
::'''Xueyi:''' Why aren't you laughing?
::'''Xueyi:''' It's a joke. Hanya said that I should try cracking more jokes when conversing with others.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} *laughs out loud*
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502100010-->
:::'''Xueyi:''' You laughed! I'm glad.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sorry! I forgot to laugh!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502100012-->
:::'''Xueyi:''' There's no need to apologize. I should have made a funnier joke.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's not a very funny joke...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502100014-->
:::'''Xueyi:''' I see. It seems I must ask Hanya for more advice.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502100015-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502100015-->
::'''Xueyi:''' Joking aside, why have you come here today? Is there something you wish to discuss?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502100002: Config/Level/Mission/5021000/Act/Act502100002.json-->
